BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 23) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Now, whenever you look up at the night sky, see if you can find Stella.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (She's the small, steady light at the edge   not the flashiest, not the biggest.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (But she's the one that makes you feel warm inside. The one that makes the dark feel less) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (scary.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (And she wants you to know: your light matters too, no matter how small it seems.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (So shine your own way, little one. The world needs exactly the kind of light that only you) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (can give.) Tj ET
