BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Because here is the beautiful truth about light:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (A candle in a dark room is more precious than a bonfire in broad daylight.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (A whisper of comfort is more powerful than a shout that nobody hears.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (And a gentle glow that says 'you are not alone' can change someone's entire night.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (That is who you are. That is what you give. And it is more than enough.) Tj ET
