BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (The Moral of the Story) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (You Are Special Just As You Are) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.4 Td (Stella learned that she didn't need to shine like everyone else to be important. Her) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.4 Td (gentle, soft light was exactly what scared and lonely people needed. You don't have to be) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.4 Td (the loudest, fastest, or brightest to matter. Your unique gifts   whether they're) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.4 Td (kindness, gentleness, listening, or simply being there   are exactly what someone in the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.4 Td (world needs. Never wish to be someone else. The world needs you, just as you are.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
