BT /F1 10 Tf 54 680.2 Td (After reading this story together, talk about these questions:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.4 Td (1. Have you ever felt like you weren't as good as someone else at something? How did that) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.4 Td (feel?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.6 Td (2. What are some things that make YOU special and different from everyone else?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.8 Td (3. Why do you think gentle things \(like a nightlight or a quiet friend\) are sometimes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 580.8 Td (better than loud, bright things?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 557.0 Td (4. If you could help someone with your own special gift, who would you help and how?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 533.2 Td (5. Can you think of a time when someone's kindness \(not loudness or brightness\) made you) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 519.2 Td (feel better?) Tj ET
